	   <tr><td colspan=2>First off, Sgt Slate is part of every young bard's initiation.&nbsp;&nbsp;If its not him its some other guard.  The catch is this - you are playing Chords of Dissonance and Sgt Slate wanders into your AoE.  He gets mad and spanks you.  Remember that your songs (most of them, anyway) have a 3 tick duration even if you stop playing it. So, you may be quiet as a mouse and suddenly get aggro for that reason.<br><br>Now, for stats, DEX helps prevent missed notes (the bard equivelent to fizzles).  DEX also helps your offensive skills go up faster.  CHA has the same affect for bards as it does for Enchanters.<br><br>For gear, since you do function part time as a melee you will need HP gear.  Try to get STA to 100 (saves you having to twist STA songs periodically). <br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
