	   <tr><td colspan=2>Keeping all your weapon skills up is important later in life. You never know when you'll get a new weapon that requires a certain skill. I was 1hs for my entire career until I picked up a Sambata War staff in my 30's that is 1hb. I had to spend a lot of time trying to get that skill up, so I grabbed a Sionaches Partisian to work on piercing at the same time. It came in real handy when PoP came out and I got my hands on a Troubadour's mace and later on, a Dirk of the Dain.<br><br>I recommend getting 1 of each weapon type (1hs, 1hb, piercing) and swap them every few days when grouping and meleeing.<br>&nbsp;<br>Selc Silverhand<br>&lt;Clan X&gt;<br>Server: The Rathe</td></tr>
