	   <tr><td colspan=2>/nods<br><br>Train them all.&nbsp;&nbsp;One way I train up my weapons skills at level 32 is Fear Kiting.  I twist<br><br>Selo's Consonant Chain<br>Angtlich's Appalling Screech<br>Jonathan's Whistling War Song<br>and occassionally I throw in a Jaxon's Jig of Vigor (when my fatigue bar gets down near 1 bubble left).<br><br>I keep Crisson's Pixie Strike mem'd in case a I need a break.<br><br>Just equip weapons. Pull with SCC.  When the mob is in range hit the fear song then JWW when they run.  Beat on them from behind and watch the weapon skills creep up.  Its not a fast way to kill mobs, generally, but it is a safe and effective way to get your weapon skills up.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
