	   <tr><td colspan=2>There's a secret path in Neriak Foreign Quarter. If you go into the troll section of town, there's a guy called... Carver something. Behind him is a false wall, that, if you follow it will bring you out behind the waterfall. If you can get by the troll, (I'd use your invisile song, or maybe tracking to con him) then you should be okay, because there are no mobs anywhere back there, and your return trip should be fine, because the Zl for the secret path is a bit away from him and anybody else.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
