	   <tr><td colspan=2>4 songs will result in a lot of drops of at least one song unless you have a really good, steady, network connection.&nbsp;&nbsp;Not everyone does.  It depends on your PC, your ISP, the speed of your connection and the response time of SonyEQ's servers.  It can also depend on which internet backbone you are connecting to and how much traffic it is handling at any given time.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
